<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>파일 확장자 제한</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <main class="container">
      <header class="header">
        <div class="header-icon" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <h1>파일 확장자 차단</h1>
      </header>

      <p class="description">
        파일확장자에 따라 특정 형식의 파일을 첨부하거나 전송하지 못하도록 제한
      </p>

      <!-- 고정 확장자 -->
      <section class="fix">
        <h2>고정 확장자</h2>
        <div class="fixed-extensions">
          <% ["bat","cmd","com","cpl","exe","scr","js"].forEach(ext => { %>
          <label class="checkbox-item">
            <input
              type="checkbox"
              name="fixed-ext"
              value="<%= ext %>"
              id="<%= ext %>"
            />
            <span><%= ext %></span>
          </label>
          <% }) %>
        </div>
      </section>

      <br />

      <!-- 커스텀 확장자 -->
      <section class="custom">
        <h2>커스텀 확장자</h2>
        <div class="input-group">
          <input
            type="text"
            id="customExtension"
            placeholder="확장자 입력"
            maxlength="20"
          />
          <button class="add-btn" id="addBtn">+추가</button>
        </div>
        <p class="error-message" id="errorMessage"></p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="custom-extensions-box">
          <p class="counter" id="counter">0/200</p>
          <div class="tags-container" id="tagsContainer"></div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <script src="/js/index.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
